{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_steam_aboutHeader.png?t=1696226987\" /><br><strong>Glyphen </strong>is an Immersive Spellcasting Adventure in which you play as a <strong>Keeper</strong>, a scholar sent to explore the ruins of a forgotten civilization. However, among the dust and the rubbles, you discover a way to draw mysterious <strong>Glyphs</strong> and invoke something that was long gone from this world: <strong>magic</strong>.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_steam_aboutTitle1.png?t=1696226987\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_spell.gif?t=1696226987\" /><br><br>Explore the ruins of <strong>Talyr ka Mot</strong> to find new Glyphs, discover their secrets and combine them into a wide variety of <strong>spells</strong>. Experiment to find new spell effects or change a simple a flame into a giant fireball, or a classic heal into a rejuvenating dome. The organic way to discover and cast spells will make YOU (more than your character) a <strong>master spellcaster</strong>, able to quickly invoke a fireball even in the face of danger. Unless you succumb to panic, lose your mind and your dexterity...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_steam_aboutTitle2.png?t=1696226987\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_KP.gif?t=1696226987\" /><br><br>Through the streets of the Outskirts to the heart of the mountain, uncover the history of the <strong>Helgemor</strong>. As part of the First Expedition, your role is to explore and understand what happened to this city and those who lived here. But beware: just because the city is abandoned doesn't mean it is without dangers. And with the powers and technology that dwell in the ruins, <strong>Talyr ka Mot</strong> could also become you and your companions' last rest...<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_steam_aboutTitle3.png?t=1696226987\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_freeze.gif?t=1696226987\" /><br><br>Between elemental reactions, movable objects and other interactive elements, Glyphen aims to give you an <strong>immersive experience</strong> through and through. Approach every obstacle your way, outsmart your enemies and use the environment to your advantage, all without any handholding. Keep your eyes open and your <strong>mind sharp</strong>.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2601170?t=1696226987","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1696226987","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1696226987","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1696226987","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2626880,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2601170/extras/gly_steam_aboutHeader.png?t=1696226987\" /><br><strong>Glyphen </strong>is an Immersive Spellcasting Adventure in which you play as a <strong>Keeper</strong>, a scholar sent to explore the ruins of a forgotten civilization. However, among the dust and the rubbles, you discover a way to draw mysterious <strong>Glyphs</strong> and invo